list.name: Default
list.comment: MultiPool renamed to CompsPool, fast_vector::shrink & fast_vector::enlarge Pool also stores aux_index for its items added: ItemPtr, ItemRefPtr, ItemAutoPtr - pointers into containers/managers PolyPool - for storing multiple types (each in its own contignuous array) with same base class SortedArray - keeps items sorted via memmoving VArray - replaces VVector & VVector2, polymorphic items in single contignuous pool (each occupies space for largest possible class) EventCb - managed by EventsHandler, multiple binding options to Functors and possibly to object

task.summary: properties declaration, hasProps type checker VVector - vector managing objects of arbitrary types via pointers Call - compile time type-conditional caller ManagerSingletons - contains single instance of each type TypeInfoManager - dynamic type info VariantCaller - calls correctly typed variant into functor
custom assert (with message & non-crashing) + minor changes
added Timer class added emscripten build
fixed bug with incorrectly setting redirect id when deleting item from unsortedvector getBase() for casting to currently set variant's bases + minor changes

VVector can be templated with types from typesPack also has addAs for specifying pointer type that is stored in vector macros for creating enums and extending enums convenience getter for typeInfo in typesPack

UnsortedVector removed instead added Array & TightArray (with holes) - has Pool & TightPool (internal struct for Array & TightArray)
Added SharedBuffer - refcounted buffer Added RoundBuffer hash funcs added to common.h Measure & BlockMeasure for debug time measurement & logging
Added SortedSet fast_vector rewrite: - cleaned - instead of mStart, mAllocEnd, mEnd now uses mStart, mSize, mCapacity - also probably a little faster
fixes for MultiPool defConstruction for MultiPool

added shorted typedefs for basic types enum macros now also define masks fixed warnings removed SimpleSet added Mask Clock inner implementation changed from std::chrono to windows specific (QueryPerformanceTimer ...) (TODO: do for linux), because chrono has shitty precision & performance

added defs for std types added Items - wraps bytes vector and acts on it as it is vector of objects free items removed from pool & tightpool (free list is interwined in data now) added DirPath Clock - fixed time measurement for Linux & Web

added added ustring - utf8 string (c++11 std::string cant be memmoved and so used in fast_vector and some other containers) string&stream utils refactored to ssu:: namespace Config class can have multiple sections added EventsHandler & EventsHandlerTyped for subscribing & emiting events added ChunkedBuffer, used in MultiPool added Items2 - facade class on bytes array with TypeInfo (calls destructors ...) added Bits - dynamic size bitset Mask class reworked to custom full static bitset BitScanner allowing fast bit looping added ObjFunc for function dispatch (faster than std::function), allowing compile time optimization
added custom profiling added F8x8 - simple fixed sized bitmap font added TestBench - for running tests and profiling them
conditionally some SDL2 dependant things (guarded by USE_SDL2 define): - SDL2TestBench for simple SDL2 window with debug overlay with profiling info - SDL2Text for drawing F8x8 texts
